)<br />\n大阪歷史博物館(谷町四丁目站9號出口)<br />\n大阪城(谷町四丁目)<br />\n心齋橋(美國村,心齋橋筋商店街)<br />\n道頓堀水上觀光船<br />\n阿倍野HARUKAS展望台(天王寺)<br />\n <br />\nDay2(Sat):   通天閣(地鐵惠美須町站)<br />\n海遊館(大阪港)<br />\n觀光船聖母瑪利亞號<br />\nHEP FIVE 摩天輪, 空中庭園展望台(梅田)<br />\n <br />\nDay3(Sun): 大阪天王寺動物園(動物園前)<br />\n天王寺(地鐵谷町線四天王寺前夕陽丘站4號出口)<br />\n電電城 (でんでんタウン) (地鐵界筋線惠美須町站出站)<br />\n <br />\nDay4(Mon): 大阪出發 &rarr; 伏見稻荷大社（伏見稻荷站下車） &rarr; 祇園花見小路（祇園四条站下車） &rarr; 法觀寺 &rarr; 石塀小路 &rarr; 高台寺 &rarr; 寧寧之道 &rarr;八坂通 &rarr; 八坂神社 &rarr; 大阪<br />\n <br />\nDay5(Tue): 難波&rarr;機場<br />\n<br />\n利申亂plan day 3可能轉去usj"},{"pid":"588544c935f58799eb6de5fa5affa92c0c4372f7","tid":388374,"uid":39847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T02:31:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人今晚係京都 搵人一齊食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係大阪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee23937269ea4da8be9f2bf522c21e0dae2e18c","tid":388374,"uid":29246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:56:05.000Z","msg":"咁都負評.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44326efa0f28c37c4b732a7c7197b53c26049144","tid":388374,"uid":9395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:28:53.000Z","msg":"飛田呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4754e4af2b07428f875f6fc0a7a0436e2aa43c4","tid":388374,"uid":29246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:55:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b730cbc497c2d7fb8f0521ec834965274b8335f1","tid":388374,"uid":29246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T11:58:30.000Z","msg":"真係無人??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/